{"tid":2267103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇永康任亞姐表演嘉賓驚現腫脹身形　最怕患癌：我個仔得3歲","createTime":"2020-11-01T23:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T16:17:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":382,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"efc2987823cbc7d8503938ee6536c95750771c4c","tid":2267103,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T23:31:41.000Z","msg":"《2020亞洲小姐香港區決賽》昨晚（1/11）在亞視總台舉行，最終由10號蔡小蝶奪冠。表演嘉賓之一的蘇永康亮相傳媒時竟現脹爆身形，他接受傳媒訪問時都認自己肥，但指之前已經減了八、九磅，而且會繼續減肥。【亞姐2020】香港賽區三甲出爐 「退選港姐」10號蔡小蝶奪冠<br />\n<br />\n體檢證沒三高 最擔心患癌<br />\n他又指，雖然現在身形腫脹，但認為「肥唔緊要，但唔好長期肥。」他坦言自己早前做了全面的身體檢查，結果身體非常健康，連三高都沒有。但他比較擔心會患癌，皆因其父親曾患胰臟癌，母親則患過直腸癌，所以為了兒子，他會頻密地接受身體檢查，「我個仔得3歲咋！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，提及好友兼前無綫監製錢國偉逝世一事時，蘇永康提到，曾相約許志安和張衛健商討如何幫錢太陳苑蔚處理身後事；他又指上星期以錢國偉名義捐獻了200個齋給老人家，當為故友做功德。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201102/399730448965570560251374.jpeg/0gDPJ3oO_yNtA76K6HkLpNdUu7jNdKLouAW5BrgFuQY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201102%2F399730448965570560251374.jpeg%2F0gDPJ3oO_yNtA76K6HkLpNdUu7jNdKLouAW5BrgFuQY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e454cafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201102/399727230193766400126793.jpeg/KR9_tbDlrXWyE8PFXlfk8AAmQ7CQCPo-1iQCXtYkAl4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201102%2F399727230193766400126793.jpeg%2FKR9_tbDlrXWyE8PFXlfk8AAmQ7CQCPo-1iQCXtYkAl4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=783fb324&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19772d65871fea1e757f1c579567743cdde49e51","tid":2267103,"uid":7763,"like":193,"dislike":0,"score":193,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face